data.description: Step into Chaparral Country Club, a charming guard-gated community nestled in the heart of Palm Desert. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit offers stunning mountain views from both inside the home and the peaceful backyard patio. With fresh paint, new flooring, and a modern AC system, it's a place you can easily transform into your ideal home. Plus, it's conveniently located just two doors down from the pool and spa.But there's more to discover. As a resident, you'll have access to a range of great amenities, including a clubhouse with a popular restaurant, a well-equipped fitness center, an 18-hole golf course, and 21 inviting pool and spa options. Tennis courts, pickleball, and a variety of social activities round out the experience. It's not just a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade. Welcome to your new beginning at Chaparral Country Club.
